metadata.name: Reign - Paranoid Earthling
metadata.description:
By [**Paranoid Earthling**](https://opensea.io/ParanoidEarthling)

[Reign](https://open.spotify.com/track/2rmWXIW6USbh7Ot83udNzA?si=6b2516d951954992) is the 6th single release by the Sri Lankan rock band  [Paranoid Earthling](https://open.spotify.com/artist/0jBbAS6xNIRo5AbDHUeeAd)  
This song is about power and ego. From the rise to the fall of an authoritarian regime in the eyes of a Megalomaniac Dictator. Inspired by historical world events.

Written and composed by: [Mirshad Buckman](https://twitter.com/Mirshad999)  

In-recording performances:  
Guitars/Bass/Vocals: Mirshad Buckman  
Drums: Harshan Gallage

Drums recorded at: Paragon Music Studio, Sri Lanka  
Guitars/Bass/Vocals recorded at: Buckman Audio, Sri Lanka 

Engineered, mixed and produced by: Mirshad Buckman  
Mastered by: Pete Maher at [Pete Maher Mastering](https://www.petemaher.com), London UK

Artwork by: [Mirshad Buckman](https://foundation.app/@Mirshad.Buckman)
